      "text": [
        "2223 - وَ مَنْ رَجَعَ مِنْ مَكَّةَ وَ هُوَ يَنْوِي اَلْحَجَّ مِنْ قَابِلٍ زِيدَ فِي عُمُرِهِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2223 - Whoever returns from Makkah intending to perform Hajj again the following year will have their lifespan increased."
